{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"网络状况 API","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Network_Information_API","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div></div>\n\n<p>网络状态 API 可以获取到系统的网络连接信息，比如说连接方式是 WiFi 还是蜂窝。应用程序可以根据此信息为用户展现不同清晰度的内容。该 API 是由 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NetworkInformation\"><code>NetworkInformation</code></a> 接口和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> 接口上新增的一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/connection\" title=\"connection\"><code>connection</code></a> 属性组成的。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"侦测连接状态变化","title":"侦测连接状态变化","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面是一个侦测用户设备连接状态变化的例子。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> connection <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>connection <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mozConnection <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>webkitConnection<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> type <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> connection<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>type<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">updateConnectionStatus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"设备的网络连接从\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> type <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"变成了\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> connection<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>type<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nconnection<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'change'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> updateConnectionStatus<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"query":"api.NetworkInformation,api.Navigator.connection","specifications":[]}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"浏览器兼容性","title":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"NetworkInformation","id":"networkinformation","isH3":true,"query":"api.NetworkInformation","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Network_Information_API/bcd.json"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Navigator.connection","id":"navigator.connection","isH3":true,"query":"api.Navigator.connection","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Network_Information_API/bcd-2.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"http://w3c.github.io/netinfo/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Network Information API Specification</a><span title=\"编辑草案(非官方)\" style=\"color:#fff;background:#e61919;display:inline-block; font-size:x-small; margin-left:6px; white-space:nowrap; padding:2px 5px;\">ED</span></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/onLine\">Online and offline events</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>window.navigator.connection</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"侦测连接状态变化","id":"侦测连接状态变化"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"网络状态 API 可以获取到系统的网络连接信息，比如说连接方式是 WiFi 还是蜂窝。应用程序可以根据此信息为用户展现不同清晰度的内容。该 API 是由 NetworkInformation 接口和 Navigator 接口上新增的一个 connection 属性组成的。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Network Information API","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/network_information_api","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/network_information_api/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Network_Information_API","title":"网络状况 API"}],"pageTitle":"网络状况 API - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}